<h1 class="mar-b-xs">Text</h1>
<h2 class="txt-gray-5 mar-t-none">Headings, paragraphs, and other text-based elements</h2>
<h2 id="demo">Demo</h2>
<code-sample>
  <h1>Heading 1</h1>
  <h2>Heading 2</h2>
  <h3>Heading 3</h3>
  <h4>Heading 4</h4>
  <h5>Heading 5</h5>
  <h6>Heading 6</h6>
  <p>This is a paragraph. And here is <span class="fnt-bold">bold text</span> and some <span class="fnt-italic">italic text</span>. More text variations can be done using the <a href="/helper-classes">helper classes</a>.</p>
  <small>This is for small print.</small>
</code-sample>
